10215908212.png" alt="image-20250308213553037"></p><p><img src="https://cloud.hkjsxb.com/20250310220029998.png" alt="image-20250308213738079"></p><h2 id="二、配置环境变量"><a href="#二、配置环境变量" class="headerlink" title="二、配置环境变量"></a>二、配置环境变量</h2><ul><li><p>安装好MySQL之后，还需要配置环境变量，这样才可以在任何目录下连接MySQL。</p></li><li><p>打开环境变量-&gt;系统变量-&gt;Path-&gt;编辑-&gt;新建-&gt;将MySQL Server的安装目录下的bin目录添加到环境变量-&gt;确定</p></li></ul><p><img src="https://cloud.hkjsxb.com/20250310215914640.png" alt="image-20250308214931436"></p><ul><li>至此完成安装</li></ul><p><img src="https://cloud.hkjsxb.com/20250310215929176.png" alt="image-20250308215255994"></p></div>]]></content>
      
      
